node.text:
UPDATE: the Plushies are officially sold out! Thank you all so much 💛💛💛 

Surprise! Plushies are back in stock baby!!! 

As all the preorders get delivered and all of your pictures come in, we've had so many questions about whether we will have more plushies available for purchase. Welllll SURPRISE! We have a *limited* amount of bonus plushies available to buy until they sell out! You can get your own through the link in my bio to purchase your own so they can lovingly watch over you and report comic ideas back to us i mean oops that's not- 

Will keep you all updated when the plushies sell out or for any other updates! 💛

If you preordered yours in spring and they haven’t arrived yet, they are on their way and should be arriving any day now! If you need more help with tracking your order or any other info, send an email to support@snapcreative.com 💛
